00067     private class RotateView extends ViewGroup implements SensorListener {
00068         private static final float SQ2 = 1.414213562373095f;
00069         private final SmoothCanvas mCanvas = new SmoothCanvas();
00070         private float mHeading = 0;
00071

00073             super(context);
00074         }
00075 
00076         public void onSensorChanged(int sensor, float[] values) {
00077             //Log.d(TAG, "x: " + values[0] + "y: " + values[1] + "z: " + values[2]);
00078             synchronized (this) {
00079                 mHeading = values[0];
00080                 invalidate();
00081             }
00082         }
00083 
00084         @Override
00085         protected void dispatchDraw(Canvas canvas) {
00086             canvas.save(Canvas.MATRIX_SAVE_FLAG);
00087             canvas.rotate(-mHeading, getWidth() * 0.5f, getHeight() * 0.5f);
00088             mCanvas.delegate = canvas;
00089             super.dispatchDraw(mCanvas);
00090             canvas.restore();
00091         }
00092 
00093         @Override
00094         protected void onLayout(boolean changed, int l, int t, int r, int b) {
00095             final int width = getWidth();
00096             final int height = getHeight();
00097             final int count = getChildCount();
00098             for (int i = 0; i < count; i++) {
00099                 final View view = getChildAt(i);
00100                 final int childWidth = view.getMeasuredWidth();
00101                 final int childHeight = view.getMeasuredHeight();
00102                 final int childLeft = (width - childWidth) / 2;
00103                 final int childTop = (height - childHeight) / 2;
00104                 view.layout(childLeft, childTop, childLeft + childWidth, childTop + childHeight);
00105             }
00106         }
00107 
00108         @Override
00109         protected void onMeasure(int widthMeasureSpec, int heightMeasureSpec) {
00110             int w = getDefaultSize(getSuggestedMinimumWidth(), widthMeasureSpec);
00111             int h = getDefaultSize(getSuggestedMinimumHeight(), heightMeasureSpec);
00112             int sizeSpec;
00113             if (w > h) {
00114                 sizeSpec = MeasureSpec.makeMeasureSpec((int) (w * SQ2), MeasureSpec.EXACTLY);
00115             } else {
00116                 sizeSpec = MeasureSpec.makeMeasureSpec((int) (h * SQ2), MeasureSpec.EXACTLY);
00117             }
00118             final int count = getChildCount();
00119             for (int i = 0; i < count; i++) {
00120                 getChildAt(i).measure(sizeSpec, sizeSpec);
00121             }
00122             super.onMeasure(widthMeasureSpec, heightMeasureSpec);
00123         }

00137     @Override
00138     public void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {

00140 
00141         mSensorManager = (SensorManager) getSystemService(SENSOR_SERVICE);
00142         mRotateView = new RotateView(this);
00143         mMapView = new MapView(this, "MapViewCompassDemo_DummyAPIKey");
00144         mRotateView.addView(mMapView);
00145         setContentView(mRotateView);
00146 
00147         mMyLocationOverlay = new MyLocationOverlay(this, mMapView);
00148         mMyLocationOverlay.runOnFirstFix(new Runnable() { public void run() {
00149             mMapView.getController().animateTo(mMyLocationOverlay.getMyLocation());
00150         }});
00151         mMapView.getOverlays().add(mMyLocationOverlay);
00152         mMapView.getController().setZoom(18);
00153         mMapView.setClickable(true);
00154         mMapView.setEnabled(true);
00155     }
